Subject: License issue
Description: Hello PingCastle, I updated PingCastlePro last month using PingCastleProSetup_3.2.1.0.zip and we have noticed that when running PingCastle.exe it is showing as the free version and version 3.2.0. This is when we select a domain to investigate and it starts to run. The .exe when you start it is showing 3.2.1 The portal shows 3.2.1 and our pro license I've checked "License" in appsettings.Production.json and can see our license in there. Could you let me know what the issue is? Kind regards, Alex
Solution_Comment__c:
<LicenseSettings

    license="" />

Updated pingastle.config. file with the license key, all is working.
